  },
  {
    question: "What does the text message say?",
    answer: "The message is entirely yours — written during setup and editable at any time. A typical damp specialist message reads: 'Thank you for calling [company name]. I am currently surveying a property and will return your call shortly. Reply with details of your damp concern for a faster response.' Adjust the wording to match your company voice and service style."
  },
  {
    question: "Does this replace AI Phone Answering?",
    answer: "They function as paired layers. Phone Answering conducts full diagnostic conversations — asking about rooms affected, wall orientation, property age, cellar access, and timber exposure. Missed Call Text Back catches the rare calls that slip past — a caller who disconnects after one ring, or a signal dead spot inside a rubble-walled cellar. Combined, every damp enquiry is retained."
